"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"In Iran, people say that every part of the capital has been hit. They hear explosions day and night as the US and Israel continue their attacks for a third day. An Iranian official has threatened to set fire to any ships passing through the Strait of Hormuz.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iran Under Attack\",            \"translated_version\": \"En Ir\u00e1n, la gente dice que cada parte de la capital ha sido golpeada. Escuchan explosiones d\u00eda y noche mientras Estados Unidos e Israel contin\u00faan sus ataques por tercer d\u00eda. Un oficial iran\u00ed ha amenazado con prender fuego a cualquier barco que pase por el Estrecho de Ormuz.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ir\u00e1n Bajo Ataque\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel has announced that its ground troops will advance in Lebanon. Meanwhile, Iranian strikes continue in the region, adding to the tension.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israel Troops Advance\",            \"translated_version\": \"Israel ha anunciado que sus tropas avanzar\u00e1n en L\u00edbano. Mientras tanto, los ataques iran\u00edes contin\u00faan en la regi\u00f3n, aumentando la tensi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tropas de Israel Avanzan\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The US defense secretary has confirmed that a US military base was hit by an Iranian missile on Sunday. This is part of the ongoing conflict involving the US, Iran, and Israel.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Base Hit\",            \"translated_version\": \"El secretario de defensa de Estados Unidos ha confirmado que una base militar de Estados Unidos fue golpeada por un misil iran\u00ed el domingo. Esto es parte del conflicto en curso que involucra a Estados Unidos, Ir\u00e1n e Israel.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Base de EE.UU. Golpeada\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Peacekeepers are providing shelter and emergency care to about 1,000 civilians near their base. This is happening amidst the ongoing conflict in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Peacekeepers Help Civilians\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los pacificadores est\u00e1n proporcionando refugio y atenci\u00f3n de emergencia a unos 1,000 civiles cerca de su base. Esto est\u00e1 sucediendo en medio del conflicto en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pacificadores Ayudan a Civiles\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Three victims and the suspected gunman were killed in a shooting on Sunday. The FBI says this incident could have links to terrorism, and more people were injured.\",            \"english_title\": \"Shooting Incident\",            \"translated_version\": \"Tres v\u00edctimas y el sospechoso fueron asesinados en un tiroteo el domingo. El FBI dice que este incidente podr\u00eda tener v\u00ednculos con el terrorismo, y m\u00e1s personas resultaron heridas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Incidente de Tiroteo\"        }    ]}"